{"tid":567937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊美大媽住酒店做呢樣嘢　驚動警察消防遭索賠","createTime":"2018-02-21T09:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T09:56:03.000Z","uid":10958,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03131c2d4e5000ba905ff0b148a31f8cf6f6031d","tid":567937,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>遊美大媽住酒店做呢樣嘢　驚動警察消防遭索賠<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=CHI180221-13929-3333-M&amp;d=1519162725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DCHI180221-13929-3333-M%26d%3D1519162725&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=f026dc91\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=CHI180221-13929-3333-M&amp;d=1519162725</a><br />\n<br />\n上海一名大媽近日跟團到美國旅遊，入住某酒店後，把洗好的衣服掛在牆上的消防警報器上，想晾乾衣服。不料翌天清晨，她在取衣架時，卻觸動到消防警報，驚動當地消防和警察部門到場。事後，她更被酒店索償2萬多元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/photo/bkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001_01b.jpg?20180221092234\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180221%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001_01b.jpg%3F20180221092234&h=0f8cde20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉大媽觸動到消防警報後，酒店房間內的噴淋全部被打開，警鈴大作。當地消防部門接報後，迅速出動5輛消防車和1輛警車，其中一輛消防車更啟動雲梯，在現場展開施救。事發突然，住客們被要求緊急逃生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/photo/bkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001_02b.jpg?20180221092234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180221%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180221092234&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=0e907bb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/photo/bkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001_02b.jpg?20180221092234</a><br />\n<br />\n消防和警方隨後向住客詢問，又逐一檢查酒店情況，共花了約3個多小時，確認現場安全後，才允許住客回房。雖然是虛驚一場，但酒店噴淋或因太久未有使用，噴淋頭裏噴出的水都是銹黃甚至是黑色，弄污了酒店內的地氈和床單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/photo/bkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001_03b.jpg?20180221092234\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180221%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20180221092234&h=d6b7122f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店方面稱，由於這次錯誤觸發報警裝置，導致酒店正常工作受極大影響，遂向該名大媽提出2萬多元人民幣的賠償。大媽則到當地警署錄口供，並委託在美國的朋友和旅行社職員處理後續事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/bkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180221%2Fbkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001.html&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=c3d7f351\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/bkncn-20180221045035285-0221_05011_001.html</a>"}]}